l%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190428%2F20666038&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8p2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=308a038b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190428%2F20666038&h=53bae071\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190428/20666038</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=bRDrzlq6GZk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbRDrzlq6GZk%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8p2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=30abbce6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=bRDrzlq6GZk&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T00:07:36.000Z","msg":"唔係咁柒掛韓狗？仲話選總統..."},{"pid":"9d5c493a589826149c3d7d6531b20303eb66abae","tid":1128493,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T00:17:27.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜承認領走2677萬補助款還開嗆 <br />\n王浩宇一句話酸爆<br />\n<br />\n2019-04-27 <br />\n  <br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕桃園市議員王浩宇今天下午在臉書發文諷刺，高雄市長韓國瑜領走了「2677萬6350元的選舉補助款，接著又想選總統，『真正發大財的其實是韓國瑜跟李佳芬』」，韓國瑜受訪坦承此事，並反嗆要王浩宇好好監督桃園市長鄭文燦。對此，王浩宇則用一句話回酸。<br />\n<br />\n面對王浩宇在臉書的爆料，<span style=\"color: red;\">韓國瑜今傍晚出席活動時大方坦言，自己的確領走2千多萬元選舉補助款，強調每一位當選人都有領一票30元的補助款</span>；韓國瑜語氣不耐反問，王浩宇「是不是要關心鄭文燦領多少錢？」、「桃園議員應該監督桃園市長」。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜更嗆說，王浩宇對桃園市長領多少錢都不告訴社會大眾，「他來管高雄市長幹嘛！」，對於韓國瑜坦承領取2000多萬的選舉補助款，還反嗆要他好好監督桃園市長鄭文燦，王浩宇則在臉書回酸，「鄭文燦施政滿意度第一名，而且沒有做四個月就要去選總統」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2772583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2772583&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8p2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=2beb0007\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2772583</a><br />\n高雄發大財定係韓國瑜發大財？"},{"pid":"5d661f0dcc1c7988b3d40a519e717aea440cb5ba","tid":1128493,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite